# Backend Structure (Main Process)

## Core Components
- Main state management: [src-main/main-state.js](mdc:src-main/main-state.js)
- Main capture functionality: [src-main/capture.js](mdc:src-main/capture.js)

## Capture Modules
- Audio capture: [src-main/captureAudio.js](mdc:src-main/captureAudio.js)
- Keystroke capture: [src-main/captureKeystrokes.js](mdc:src-main/captureKeystrokes.js)
- Window capture: [src-main/captureWindows.js](mdc:src-main/captureWindows.js)
- Screenshot capture: [src-main/captureScreenshots.js](mdc:src-main/captureScreenshots.js)

## Key Features
- Window tracking
- Keystroke monitoring
- Audio recording
- Screenshot capture
- System integration

## Dependencies
- Uses `active-win` for window tracking
- Uses `node-global-key-listener` for keystroke monitoring
- Uses `electron-store` for persistent storage
- Uses `electron-log` for logging
